ADDITIONAL NOTICE - HARDWARE RISK

This software drives a CPU stress workload and is intended to be used while
the user manually applies overclocking and/or undervolting settings (e.g. AMD
Ryzen Curve Optimizer / PBO, memory overclocking). Overclocking and
undervolting can cause system instability, data loss, and permanent hardware
damage, and may void your hardware warranty. You use this software, and you
change any such settings, entirely AT YOUR OWN RISK. The author accepts no
responsibility or liability for any damage of any kind. See the "Disclaimer"
section of the README for details.

This software does NOT include y-cruncher. y-cruncher is a separate program
by Alexander J. Yee with its own license; you must download it yourself.
